MongoDB storage units require a configuration
of the form:

storage_config={
    'type': 'aiomongo',
    'mongo': {'host': 'localhost', 'port': 27017}
}

one can refer to system environment variables via:

storage_config={
    'type': 'aiomongo',
    'mongo': {
        'host': {'env': 'MONGO_HOSTNAME',
                 'default':'localhost'},
        'port': 27017}
    }
}

